name: Get Out of My Kitchen
description:
Made for the Comp-3 Jam Butty 2020 - Bugs game Jam, Hosted by Comp-3 Interactive · #comp3jambutty

I present, "Get Out of My Kitchen!"

One day, a lady's kitchen is infested with bugs. Help her eliminate the vicious threat by stomping on these pests and clearing her kitchen from its invaders.

Enjoy, I really enjoyed working on this one. Expect a devlog soon.

Regards,

BurterButterBeans Studio 2020
